data.name: lHelp.Text
data.value:
Drag&&Drop below the folder you want to target, OR Have the path copied in clipboard (copy/paste) OR used F4 to select it.
If no files are shown in one of the pannes, please update the filters. Use "*.extension" and "|" (pipe) to add multiple filters.
Press F1 to auto-detect matches. If this fails used F8 to clear incorrect matches and proceed to manual matching. Use TAB key to navigate between panels and SPACE to check the left / right match. Press Enter to seal the match and continue with next match.
Use Rename -> if you want to keep the left names and overwrite the right ones. Or the other way around. Use Ctrl + Shift + Arrow in order to push file names to the direction of the arrow.
Click this message to close it. Press Help to show it again.
